name: TK_9714
content:
TK_9714 was the designation of a human stormtrooper who served the Galactic Empire. At one point, TK_9714 rode in a Lambda-class T-4a shuttle, where they disliked the lack of windows and wasn't allowed to sit in the front. TK_9714 posted a two star review of the shuttle where these factors were pointed out, and the review was eventually published in a book written by Poe Dameron.
TK_9714 was mentioned in the 2022 non-canon reference book LEGO Star Wars Awesome Vehicles.
